:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-row-colors-addon/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-row-colors-addon/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 27 Dec 2022 18:21:23 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=394336\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:503:\"<p>Organize your Page Builder rows with custom background colors. Page Builder offers five admin row background colors to help visually organize your pages. The Custom Row Colors Addon lets you add, remove, order, and name your Page Builder admin row background colors.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-row-colors-addon/\">Announcing the Custom Row Colors Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7407:\"<p>Organize your Page Builder rows with custom background colors. Page Builder offers five admin row background colors to help visually organize your pages. The Custom Row Colors Addon lets you add, remove, order, and name your Page Builder admin row background colors.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_394337\" style=\"width: 1856px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-394337\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1846\" height=\"1158\" class=\"size-full wp-image-394337\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors.png 1846w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-300x188.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-699x438.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-768x482.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-1536x964.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-1050x659.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-313x196.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1846px) 100vw, 1846px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-394337\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Page Builder offers five admin row background colors to help visually organize your pages.</p></div>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<p>Go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Custom Row Colors</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Settings</span></span> to manage your Page Builder admin row background colors.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_394239\" style=\"width: 2740px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-394239\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2730\" height=\"940\" class=\"size-full wp-image-394239\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors.png 2730w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-300x103.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-699x241.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-768x264.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-1536x529.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-2048x705.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-1050x362.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-313x108.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2730px) 100vw, 2730px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-394239\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Manage Page Builder row background colors from SiteOrigin > Premium Addons > Custom Row Colors.</p></div>\n<p>Click the Add button to add a new row background color. For existing row background colors, the icons on the right function as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Down Arrow: Opens the row background color.</li>\n<li>Page Icon: Duplicates the row background color.</li>\n<li>Close Icon: Deletes the background row color.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Click, hold, and drag to reorder your row background colors.</p>\n<p>The following fields are available when adding a new row background color:</p>\n<p><strong>Name</strong><br />\nAdd a name for the row background color. This is a required field.</p>\n<p><strong>Active Color</strong><br />\nSelect the row background active color.</p>\n<p><strong>Cell Divider</strong><br />\nSelect the row background cell divider color.</p>\n<p><strong>Cell Divider Hover</strong><br />\nSelect the row background cell divider hover color.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_394246\" style=\"width: 2740px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-394246\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2730\" height=\"1480\" class=\"size-full wp-image-394246\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color.png 2730w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-300x163.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-699x379.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-768x416.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-1536x833.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-2048x1110.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-1050x569.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-313x170.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2730px) 100vw, 2730px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-394246\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The above fields are available when adding a new row background color.</p></div>\n<h3>Applying Row Background Colors</h3>\n<p>Edit any page using Page Builder or a Page Builder Layout Block to apply row background colors. Click the wrench icon to edit a row. Select the color swatch you&#8217;d like to apply as the row background color.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_394243\" style=\"width: 1940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-394243\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1930\" height=\"841\" class=\"size-full wp-image-394243\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch.png 1930w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-300x131.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-699x305.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-768x335.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-1536x669.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-1050x458.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-313x136.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1930px) 100vw, 1930px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-394243\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Click the wrench icon to edit a row and select a background color swatch.</p></div>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/custom-row-colors/\">Custom Row Colors Addon Documentation</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium\">Find Out More About Siteorigin Premium</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for reading. Please, let us know if you have any queries or requests. We hope you find the Custom Row Colors Addon useful.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-row-colors-addon/\">Announcing the Custom Row Colors Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://sit