licit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:488:\"<p>We\'re excited to announce the SiteOrigin Blog Widget and SiteOrigin Premium Blog Addon. Display your blog posts in a list or grid. Choose from one of the following beautifully designed templates; Standard, Grid, Offset, Alternate, Masonry, or Portfolio.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-siteorigin-blog-widget/\">Announcing the SiteOrigin Blog Widget</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4293:\"<p>We&#8217;re excited to announce the SiteOrigin Blog Widget and SiteOrigin Premium Blog Addon. Display your blog posts in a list or grid. Choose from one of the following beautifully designed templates; Standard, Grid, Offset, Alternate, Masonry, or Portfolio.</p>\n<p>The Blog Widget is ready to be used anywhere:</p>\n<p><strong>Page Builder:</strong> Insert widgets in Page Builder by SiteOrigin in either the Classic Editor or Page Builder Layout Block in the Block Editor.<br />\n<strong>Block Editor:</strong> 100% Block Editor compatible. Insert widgets using the SiteOrigin Widgets Block featuring a live widget search form.<br />\n<strong>Theme and Plugin Widget Areas:</strong> Insert widgets into any theme or plugin widget area.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_385487\" style=\"width: 1900px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-385487\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1890\" height=\"1392\" class=\"size-full wp-image-385487\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings.png 1890w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-300x221.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-699x515.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-768x566.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-1536x1131.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-1050x773.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-313x231.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1890px) 100vw, 1890px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-385487\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The available Settings and Design options change based on the template selected.</p></div>\n<h4>Blog Widget Templates Demo Links</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-standard-template/\">Standard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-grid-template/\">Grid</a></a>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-offset-template/\">Offset</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-alternate-template/\">Alternate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-masonry-template/\">Masonry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-portfolio-template/\">Portfolio</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>SiteOrigin Premium Blog Addon</h3>\n<p>The Blog Addon introduces the following settings to the Blog Widget:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Excerpt Trim Indicator: Customize the excerpt trim indicator. Defaults to <code>...</code></li>\n<li>Post Read More Link Text: Customize the Post Excerpt or the Full Post Content read more text.</li>\n<li>Post Date Format: Select the post meta date format.</li>\n<li>Pagination: Adds three additional pagination styles, Previous &#8211; Next, Load More, and Infinite Scrolling.</li>\n<li>Pagination Page Reload: Select the pagination page reload style. Choose between Standard and Ajax.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>More settings and features will be added in the future as we receive feedback and requests from our users.</p>\n<h4>SiteOrigin Premium Blog Addon Pagination Demos</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/blog-prev-next/\">Previous &#8211; Next Pagination with Ajax Page Reloading</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/blog-load-more/\">Load More Pagination with Ajax Reloading</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/blog-infinite-scrolling/\">Infinite Scrolling Pagination (with Ajax Reloading)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/blog-widget/\">Blog Widget Documentation</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/blog/\">Premium Blog Addon Documentation</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for reading. Please, let us know if you have any queries or requests. We hope you find the Blog Widget useful.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-siteorigin-blog-widget/\">Announcing the SiteOrigin Blog Widget</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-siteorigin-blog-widget/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"12\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Stop Spam With Really Simple CAPTCHA\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://siteorigin.com/stop-spam-with-really-simple-captcha/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://siteorigin.com/stop-spam-with-really-simple-captcha/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 24 Jun 2022 18:28:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=373568\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:686:\"<p>The <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/so-widgets-bundle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SiteOrigin Contact Form Widget</a> now includes support for the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/really-simple-captcha/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Really Simple CAPTCHA</a> plugin authored by Takayuki Miyoshi. If you\'re a user running a website in Germany, you\'ll be happy to know that you can stop contact form spam while complying with the DSGVO.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/stop-spam-with-really-simple-captcha/\">Stop Spam With Really Simple CAPTCHA</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4437:\"<p>The <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/so-widgets-bundle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SiteOrigin Contact Form Widget</a> now includes support for the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/really-simple-captcha/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Really Simple CAPTCHA</a> plugin authored by Takayuki Miyoshi. If you&#8217;re a user running a website in Germany, you&#8217;ll be happy to know that you can stop contact form spam while complying with the DSGVO. If you&#8217;d like to add a CAPTCHA to your SiteOrigin Contact Form or if you&#8217;d like to switch from Google&#8217;s reCAPTCHA service, read on to find out more.</p>\n<p>1. To get started, make sure you have the SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle plugin installed and activated. The Widgets Bundle can be installed from <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Add New</span></span>.</p>\n<p>2. Once activated, go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin Widgets</span></span> to activate the Contact Form Widget.</p>\n<p>3. Insert or edit an existing Contact Form Widget. The Contact Form Widget is ready to be inserted anywhere.</p>\n<p><strong>Page Builder:</strong> Insert widgets in Page Builder by SiteOrigin in either the Classic Editor or Page Builder Layout Block in the Block Editor.<br />\n<strong>Block Editor:</strong> 100% Block Editor compatible. Insert widgets using the SiteOrigin Widgets Block featuring a live widget search form.<br />\n<strong>Theme and Plugin Widget Areas:</strong> Insert widgets into any theme or plugin widget area.</p>\n<p>4. Once editing your Contact Form Widget, go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Spam Protection</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Really Simple CAPTCHA</span></span> and enable the <strong>Add Really Simple CAPTCHA</strong> setting. The following additional settings are available:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Background Color</li>\n<li>Text Color</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_373611\" style=\"width: 1952px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-373611\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1942\" height=\"1294\" class=\"size-full wp-image-373611\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha.png 1942w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-300x200.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-699x466.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-768x512.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-1536x1023.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-1050x700.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-313x209.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-720x480.png 720w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-272x182.png 272w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1942px) 100vw, 1942px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-373611\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Open the Spam Protection settings section to enable the Really Simple CAPTCHA.</p></div>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/contact/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">View a Demo</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/contact-form-widget/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SiteOrigin Contact Form Widget Documentation</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for reading. If you have any queries or requests, please, let us know in the comments below.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/stop-spam-with-really-simple-captcha/\">Stop Spam With Really Simple CAPTCHA</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://siteorigin.com/stop-spam-with-really-simple-captcha/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"Link to Directly to Slides, Tabs, and Accordion Panels\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://siteorigin.com/link-to-directly-to-slides-tabs-and-accordion-panels/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"https://siteorigin.com/link-to-directly-to-slides-tabs-and-accordion-panels/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 28 May 2022 11:02:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=370097\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:619:\"<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/?featured_addon=plugin/anchor-id\">SiteOrigin Premium</a> <code>1.32.0</code> introduces the Anchor ID Addon. Link users directly to SiteOrigin Slides, Tabs, and Accordion panels. Once enabled, a unique anchor ID is added to the page URL corresponding to each SiteOrigin Slide, Tab, and Accordion panel.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/link-to-directly-to-slides-tabs-and-accordion-panels/\">Link to Directly to Slides, Tabs, and Accordion Panels</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3686:\"<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/?featured_addon=plugin/anchor-id\">SiteOrigin Premium</a> <code>1.32.0</code> introduces the Anchor ID Addon. Link users directly to SiteOrigin Slides, Tabs, and Accordion panels. Once enabled, a unique anchor ID is added to the page URL corresponding to each SiteOrigin Slide, Tab, and Accordion panel. The unique anchor allows for direct linking to specific content within each widget.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_370222\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-370222\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-699x599.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"599\" class=\"size-large wp-image-370222\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-699x599.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-300x257.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-768x658.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-1050x900.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-313x268.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor.png 1244w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-370222\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Enable the Anchor setting and enter a custom ID.</p></div>\n<p>The following widgets are supported:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Accordion</li>\n<li>Hero</li>\n<li>Layout Slider</li>\n<li>Slider</li>\n<li>Tabs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find the Anchor ID valuable if you&#8217;ve used any of the above widgets to condense content. Frequently Asked Questions or a Table of Contents are two possible use cases.</p>\n<p><strong>Link Demo</strong><br />\nThe following URL will link to the third Accordion panel <a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/anchor-id/#accordion-panel-three\">https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/anchor-id/#accordion-panel-three</a>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_370230\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-370230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-699x254.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"254\" class=\"size-large wp-image-370230\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-699x254.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-300x109.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-768x279.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-1536x557.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-2048x743.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-1050x381.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-313x114.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-370230\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Our demo link opens the third Accordion panel.</p></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/anchor-id/\">View the Addon Documentation</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">Find Out More About SiteOrigin Premium</a>.</p>\n<p>Thanks for reading. If you have any queries or requests, please, don&#8217;t hesitate to reach out.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/link-to-directly-to-slides-tabs-and-accordion-panels/\">Link to Directly to Slides, Tabs, and Accordion Panels</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"https://siteorigin.com/link-to-directly-to-slides-tabs-and-accordion-panels/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"Create Background Patterns for Your Website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://siteorigin.com/create-background-patterns-for-your-website/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://siteorigin.com/create-background-patterns-for-your-website/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 17 May 2022 19:30:10 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=368529\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:548:\"<p>We\'re excited to announce that we\'ve completely revamped the SiteOrigin Background Image Generator. The new site is super fast and easy to use. Design the perfect texture or pattern image for your website in just a few steps. Give it a try at <a href=\"https://bg.siteorigin.com\">bg.siteorigin.com</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/create-background-patterns-for-your-website/\">Create Background Patterns for Your Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3011:\"<p>We&#8217;re excited to announce that we&#8217;ve completely revamped the SiteOrigin Background Image Generator. The new site is super fast and easy to use. Design the perfect texture or pattern image for your website in just a few steps. Background images are available for download in two different PNG sizes. The Saved Steps section lets you capture a snapshot of your settings so you can experiment without losing your work. Give it a try at <a href=\"https://bg.siteorigin.com\">bg.siteorigin.com</a>.</p>\n<h3>Using the Background Image Generator</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Use the Color setting to select your base color.</li>\n<li>Use the Pattern column on the left to select your background pattern.</li>\n<li>Use the Overlay column on the right to select your background overlay filter.</li>\n<li>The Invert toggle switch inverts the pattern and overlay colors.</li>\n<li>Adjust your chosen pattern with the Pattern Intensity setting.</li>\n<li>Adjust your chosen overlay filter with the Noise setting.</li>\n<li>Ready to use your background image? Click the Download image button to download a 150 x 150 PNG image.</li>\n<li>Click the @2x button to download a 300 x 300 PNG version.</li>\n<li>Use the Saved Steps section to take a snapshot of your settings. Click the + icon to take a snapshot; a pattern image will be added to the Saved Steps section. Click on the pattern image to load the saved settings. Hover over the pattern image and click the remove icon to remove the snapshot.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Using Background Images</h3>\n<p>Most themes support a background image. To add yours, navigate to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Appearance</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Customize</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Background Image</span></span>. Click Select Image, upload your background image, click Choose Image, and Publish.</p>\n<p>Page Builder supports background images for rows, cells, and widgets.</p>\n<p><strong>Row Background Images</strong><br />\nEdit a row, open the Design section on the right, and locate the Background Image setting.</p>\n<p><strong>Cell Background Images</strong><br />\nEdit a row and click the cell you&#8217;d like to edit. Locate the Cell Styles section in the right column, the Cell Styles setting section will appear once you click on a cell. Open the Design section and add a background image via the Background Image setting.</p>\n<p><strong>Widget Background Images</strong><br />\nEdit a widget, open the Design section on the right and locate the Background Image setting.</p>\n<p>If you have any questions, comments, or requests, please, let us know in the comments below. Thanks for reading!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/create-background-patterns-for-your-website/\">Create Background Patterns for Your Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://siteorigin.com/create-background-patterns-for-your-website/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Introducing the Lottie Player Widget\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-the-lottie-player-widget/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-the-lottie-player-widget/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 29 Apr 2022 10:35:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"lottie player\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=365789\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:584:\"<p>We\'re excited to announce the SiteOrigin Lottie Player Widget. Capture user attention and bring your pages to life with Lottie animations. Activate the Lottie Player widget at Plugins &#62; SiteOrigin Widgets. A Lottie is a JSON-based animation file format that enables designers to ship animations on any platform as easily as shipping static assets.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-the-lottie-player-widget/\">Introducing the Lottie Player Widget</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8013:\"<div id=\"pl-365789\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-365789-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-365789-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-365789-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"\n			\n		>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>We\'re excited to announce the SiteOrigin Lottie Player Widget. Capture user attention and bring your pages to life with Lottie animations. Activate the Lottie Player widget at <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin Widgets</span></span>.</p>\n<p><em>A Lottie is a JSON-based animation file format that enables designers to ship animations on any platform as easily as shipping static assets. They are small files that work on any device and can scale up or down without pixelation.</em><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lottiefiles.com/what-is-lottie\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://lottiefiles.com/what-is-lottie</a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_365899\" style=\"width: 1856px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-365899\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/so-lottie-player-widget.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1846\" height=\"1152\" class=\"size-full wp-image-365899\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/so-lottie-player-widget.png 1846w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/so-lottie-player-widget-300x187.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/so-lottie-player-widget-699x436.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/so-lottie-player-widget-768x479.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/so-lottie-player-widget-1536x959.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/so-lottie-player-widget-1050x655.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/so-lottie-player-widget-313x195.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1846px) 100vw, 1846px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-365899\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">SiteOrigin Lottie Player Widget interface.</p></div>\n<p>The Lottie Player Widget is ready to be used anywhere:</p>\n<p><strong>Page Builder:</strong> Insert widgets in Page Builder by SiteOrigin in either the Classic Editor or Page Builder Layout Block in the Block Editor.<br />\n<strong>Block Editor:</strong> 100% Block Editor compatible. Insert widgets using the SiteOrigin Widgets Block featuring a live widget search form.<br />\n<strong>Theme and Plugin Widget Areas:</strong> Insert widgets into any theme or plugin widget area.</p>\n<h4>Settings</h4>\n<p><strong>Lottie File</strong><br />\nUpload or select your Lottie JSON file.</p>\n<p><strong>Autoplay</strong><br />\nEnable to autoplay the the animation.</p>\n<p><strong>Controls</strong><br />\nEnable to display the player\'s controls.</p>\n<p><strong>Loop</strong><br />\nEnable to loop the animation.</p>\n<p><strong>Destination URL</strong><br />\nEnter a destination URL to link your animation.</p>\n<p><strong>Open in a new window</strong><br />\nEnable to open the destination URL in a new window.</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-365789-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-365789-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-365789-1-0-0\" class=\"widget_text so-panel widget widget_custom_html panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" ><div class=\"textwidget custom-html-widget\"><h3>Lottie Animation Demo</h3></div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-365789-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-365789-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell panel-grid-cell-mobile-last\" ><div id=\"panel-365789-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-lottie-player panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-lottie-player so-widget-sow-lottie-player-default-d75171398898-365789\"\n			\n		>\n<div class=\"sow-lottie-player\" >\n		<lottie-player\n		class=\"sow-lottie-player\"\n		autoplay controls loop count=\"4\" direction=\"1\" speed=\"1\" mode=\"normal\" 		src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/103589-negocios124.json\"\n	>\n	</lottie-player>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-365789-2-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell panel-grid-cell-empty\" ></div></div><div id=\"pg-365789-3\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-365789-3-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-365789-3-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"\n			\n		>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h3>SiteOrigin Premium Lottie Player Addon</h3>\n<p>SiteOrigin Premium users can immediately take advantage of the Lottie Player Addon. Head over to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span></span> to activate the Lottie Player Addon. Customize and enhance your Lottie Player with the following additional settings.</p>\n<p><strong>Count</strong><br />\nNumber of times to loop the animation.</p>\n<p><strong>Direction</strong><br />\nThe direction of the animation. The Direction setting is available when Animation Mode is set to Normal.</p>\n<p><strong>Speed</strong><br />\nThe animation speed. 1 is 100% - 0 is 0%.</p>\n<p><strong>Animation Mode</strong><br />\nThe animation mode to use. Choose from Normal, Bounce, Scroll, Cursor Position, Click, Hover, Toggle, Hold, and Toggle Hold.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_365905\" style=\"width: 1258px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-365905\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/lottie-premium-settings.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1248\" height=\"764\" class=\"size-full wp-image-365905\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/lottie-premium-settings.png 1248w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/lottie-premium-settings-300x184.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/lottie-premium-settings-699x428.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/lottie-premium-settings-768x470.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/lottie-premium-settings-1050x643.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/lottie-premium-settings-313x192.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1248px) 100vw, 1248px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-365905\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lottie Player Addon additional settings.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-365789-4\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-365789-4-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-365789-4-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"4\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"\n			\n		>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://lottiefiles.com/featured\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Free Lottie Animations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/lottie-player-widget/\">SiteOrigin Lottie Player Widget Documentation</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/getting-started/\">SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle Documentation</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/lottie-player/\">SiteOrigin Premium Lottie Player Addon Documentation</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for reading. If you have any comments or questions, please, let us know in the comments section below.</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-the-lottie-player-widget/\">Introducing the Lottie Player Widget</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-the-lottie-player-widget/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"Setup a Continuous Scrolling Logo Carousel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://siteorigin.com/setup-a-continuous-scrolling-logo-carousel/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://siteorigin.com/setup-a-continuous-scrolling-logo-carousel/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 20 Mar 2022 19:40:45 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Tutorial\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"tutorial\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=358941\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:484:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Post Carousel Widget now includes <strong>continuous scrolling</strong>. Continuous scrolling is perfect for logo carousels. If you\'d like to feature a list of your client\'s logos and link each logo to a case study, read on!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/setup-a-continuous-scrolling-logo-carousel/\">Setup a Continuous Scrolling Logo Carousel</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7722:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Post Carousel Widget now includes <strong>continuous scrolling</strong>. Continuous scrolling is perfect for logo carousels. If you&#8217;d like to feature a list of your client&#8217;s logos and link each logo to a case study, read on!</p>\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/so-widgets-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle Plugin</a></li>\n<li>Optional: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/siteorigin-panels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Page Builder by SiteOrigin Plugin</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>To make use of this widget, go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin Widgets</span></span> to activate the SiteOrigin Post Carousel Widget.</p>\n<h4>Creating a Custom Post Type for Your Clients</h4>\n<p>The Post Carousel Widget <strong>Posts Query</strong> section offers the ability to filter your WordPress posts using tags, categories, or post types. We&#8217;ll be using the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/custom-post-type-ui/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Custom Post Type UI</a> plugin to create a new post type for our clients.</p>\n<p>&#8211; Go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Add New</span></span>. Search for, install and active <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/custom-post-type-ui/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Custom Post Type UI</a> by WebDevStudios.<br />\n&#8211; Go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">CPT UI</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Add/Edit Post Types</span></span><br />\n&#8211; Add a new post type. We&#8217;ve created a post type called <code>clients</code> for this demo.</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-post-type.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1860\" height=\"1321\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-359267\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-post-type.jpg 1860w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-post-type-300x213.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-post-type-699x496.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-post-type-768x545.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-post-type-1536x1091.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-post-type-1050x746.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-post-type-313x222.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1860px) 100vw, 1860px\" /></p>\n<p>&#8211; Click the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Add Post Types</span></span> button to complete the process.</p>\n<h4>Adding Your Clients</h4>\n<p>&#8211; Locate the Clients menu item in your main WordPress menu. Hover over the menu item and click <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Add New</span></span>.<br />\n&#8211; Add a Post title, Contents, and a Featured Image. Click Publish.</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-client-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2250\" height=\"1617\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-359539\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-client-1.jpg 2250w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-client-1-300x216.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-client-1-699x502.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-client-1-768x552.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-client-1-1536x1104.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-client-1-2048x1472.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-client-1-1050x755.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/add-new-client-1-313x225.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2250px) 100vw, 2250px\" /></p>\n<p>&#8211; In the above example, our client&#8217;s name is Mountland. We&#8217;ve added placeholder text for the client study. The client logo has been uploaded as the Featured Image.<br />\n&#8211; Add your remaining clients via <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Clients</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">New</span></span>.</p>\n<h4>Insert the Post Carousel Widget</h4>\n<p>Head over to Pages and edit the page you&#8217;d like to insert the Post Carousel Widget on. Alternatively, go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Appearance</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Widgets</span></span> to insert the Post Carousel Widget in a theme or plugin widget area.</p>\n<p>The Post Carousel Widget is ready to be used anywhere:</p>\n<p><strong>Page Builder:</strong> Insert widgets in Page Builder by SiteOrigin in either the Classic Editor or Page Builder Layout Block in the Block Editor.<br />\n<strong>Block Editor:</strong> 100% Block Editor compatible. Insert widgets using the SiteOrigin Widgets Block featuring a live widget search form.<br />\n<strong>Theme and Plugin Widget Areas:</strong> Insert widgets into any theme or plugin widget area.</p>\n<p>Once inserted, edit the Post Carousel Widget and open the Settings section. Enable Loop Items, Autoplay, and Autoplay Continuous Scroll. Finally, open the Post Query section, and select Clients as the Post Type.</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-post-type.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2480\" height=\"954\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-359541\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-post-type.jpg 2480w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-post-type-300x115.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-post-type-699x269.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-post-type-768x295.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-post-type-1536x591.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-post-type-2048x788.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-post-type-1050x404.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-post-type-313x120.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2480px) 100vw, 2480px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/continuous-scrolling-client-carousel/\">View the Demo</a>.</p>\n<p>Thanks for reading. </p>\n<p>If you&#8217;d like additional Post Carousel themes, please, consider <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/?featured_addon=plugin/carousel\">SiteOrigin Premium</a>. We recently added an <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-post-carousel-overlay-theme/\">Overlay Theme</a> with more themes to follow soon.</p>\n<h3>Useful Links</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/post-carousel-widget/\">SiteOrigin Post Carousel Widget Documentation</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/carousel/\">SiteOrigin Premium Post Carousel Addon Documentation</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/setup-a-continuous-scrolling-logo-carousel/\">Setup a Continuous Scrolling Logo Carousel</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://siteorigin.com/setup-a-continuous-scrolling-logo-carousel/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"Announcing the Post Carousel Overlay Theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-post-carousel-overlay-theme/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-post-carousel-overlay-theme/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 08 Mar 2022 16:18:35 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=357704\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:628:\"<p>We\'re excited to announce a new theme within the SiteOrigin Post Carousel Widget, <strong>Overlay</strong>. Post featured images are boldly displayed at <code>360px</code> wide and <code>460px</code> high. Post titles are overlaid with a subtle background gradient. Post categories are positioned above the post title as links. Carousel navigation is offered as both dots and arrows.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-post-carousel-overlay-theme/\">Announcing the Post Carousel Overlay Theme</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6660:\"<p>We&#8217;re excited to announce a new theme within the SiteOrigin Post Carousel Widget, <strong>Overlay</strong>. Post featured images are boldly displayed at <code>360px</code> wide and <code>460px</code> high. Post titles are overlaid with a subtle background gradient. Post categories are positioned above the post title as links. Carousel navigation is offered as both dots and arrows.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/post-carousel-overlay-theme/\">View the Overlay Theme Demo</a>.</p>\n<p>Choose your level of customization. Overlay&#8217;s beautiful design is ready to be inserted with little to no changes. Alternatively, dive in and customize every aspect of the design and functionality to make it your own. The choice is yours.</p>\n<p>The Overlay theme is available as part of the SiteOrigin Premium Carousel Addon. The Carousel Addon initially included Layout Builder and Anchor ID functionality for the Anything Carousel Widget. We&#8217;re excited to expand the addon by introducing a new theme for the Post Carousel Widget.</p>\n<p>The Overlay theme was created by Ricardo Salazar, who also designed the SiteOrigin Unwind and Corp themes and the Anything Carousel base theme, to name just a few. Work started in Figma before making its way to Alex at SiteOrigin for coding.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_357715\" style=\"width: 2570px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-357715\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/figma-overlay-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"949\" class=\"size-full wp-image-357715\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/figma-overlay-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/figma-overlay-300x111.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/figma-overlay-699x259.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/figma-overlay-768x285.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/figma-overlay-1536x569.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/figma-overlay-2048x759.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/figma-overlay-1050x389.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/figma-overlay-313x116.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-357715\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Overlay theme design in Figma; before coding began.</p></div>\n<h4>Usage Instructions</h4>\n<p>With the SiteOrigin Premium plugin activated; head over to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span></span> within your WordPress installation. Activate the Carousel Addon if it isn&#8217;t already activated. Next, edit a page or post and insert a SiteOrigin Post Carousel Widget. Edit the Post Carousel Widget and open the Design settings section. Locate the <strong>Theme</strong> setting and select <strong>Overlay</strong> from the drop-down menu.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_357722\" style=\"width: 2570px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-357722\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-overlay-settings-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1373\" class=\"size-full wp-image-357722\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-overlay-settings-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-overlay-settings-300x161.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-overlay-settings-699x375.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-overlay-settings-768x412.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-overlay-settings-1536x824.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-overlay-settings-2048x1098.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-overlay-settings-1050x563.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/post-carousel-overlay-settings-313x168.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-357722\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Post Carousel Overlay Settings</p></div>\n<h4>More Themes to Follow</h4>\n<p>New themes are soon on the way for both the Post and Anything Carousel Widgets!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_357736\" style=\"width: 2570px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-357736\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/next-carousel-theme-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1183\" class=\"size-full wp-image-357736\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/next-carousel-theme-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/next-carousel-theme-300x139.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/next-carousel-theme-699x323.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/next-carousel-theme-768x355.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/next-carousel-theme-1536x710.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/next-carousel-theme-2048x947.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/next-carousel-theme-1050x485.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/next-carousel-theme-313x145.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-357736\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A yet to be named new theme for the SiteOrigin Post Carousel Widget.</p></div>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/post-carousel-overlay-theme/\">Overlay Theme Demo</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/post-carousel-widget/\">SiteOrigin Post Carousel Widget Documentation</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/carousel/\">SiteOrigin Premium Carousel Addon Documentation</a>.</p>\n<p>Thanks for reading. If you have any comments, queries, or requests, please, let us know in the comments below. Free support is available on the <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/thread\">SiteOrigin Forum</a>. You can reach our premium support desk via email at <a href=\"mailto:support@siteorigin.com\">support@siteorigin.com</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-post-carousel-overlay-theme/\">Announcing the Post Carousel Overlay Theme</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-post-carousel-overlay-theme/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"Unwind: Expanded Video Post Format Support\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://siteorigin.com/unwind-expanded-video-post-format-support/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://siteorigin.com/unwind-expanded-video-post-format-support/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 16 Feb 2022 19:11:40 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=354314\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:560:\"<p>SiteOrigin Unwind is a modern theme for creators. Unwind version <code>1.9.0</code> offers expanded support for the Video post type. The Video post type searches for a video at the beginning of the post. If a video is found, the post featured image is replaced by the video on both the archive and single post pages.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/unwind-expanded-video-post-format-support/\">Unwind: Expanded Video Post Format Support</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2309:\"<p>SiteOrigin Unwind is a modern theme for creators. Unwind version <code>1.9.0</code> offers expanded support for the Video post type. The Video post type searches for a video at the beginning of the post. If a video is found, the post featured image is replaced by the video on both the archive and single post pages. The featured image is still available for use elsewhere such as in a post carousel or on the search results page.</p>\n<h3>Video Post Type Support</h3>\n<p>The following video instances are supported:</p>\n<p><strong>Classic Editor</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>First oEmbed video link (e.g. YouTube).</li>\n<li>Page Builder: The first row will be checked for a SiteOrigin Video Player widget if Page Builder is activated.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Block Editor</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>First oEmbed video link (ie. YouTube).</li>\n<li>If the first block on the page is a SiteOrigin Layout Block, the first row will be checked for a SiteOrigin Video Player widget.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Prior to the <code>1.9.0</code> update the Video post type only support the first oEmbed video link (e.g. YouTube) in the Classic Editor.</p>\n<h4>Demo</h4>\n<p>For a demo of the Video post type in action, please, see https://demo.siteorigin.com/unwind/. Scroll down to the <strong>Video Post</strong> heading. The single post page can be viewed <a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/unwind/video-post/\">here</a>. </p>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<p>Unwind Post Format <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/unwind-documentation/post-formats/\">Documentation</a>.<br />\nInterested in the programming and testing that went into this update? View the <a href=\"https://github.com/siteorigin/siteorigin-unwind/pull/313\">pull request</a> on Github.</p>\n<h3>Get the Complete SiteOrigin Experience With Premium</h3>\n<p>SiteOrigin Premium removes the Unwind footer attribution link and adds Ajax comments. Ajax comments allow users to post comments without the page reloading; a great way to keep the comments flowing. <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">Find out more</a> about SiteOrigin Premium.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/unwind-expanded-video-post-format-support/\">Unwind: Expanded Video Post Format Support</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://siteorigin.com/unwind-expanded-video-post-format-support/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"Dark Theme Now Available in SiteOrigin CSS\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://siteorigin.com/dark-theme-now-available-in-siteorigin-css/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://siteorigin.com/dark-theme-now-available-in-siteorigin-css/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 15 Jan 2022 14:59:58 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lan