y click a button and then you get Your Adot eCommerce WordPress Theme installed</li>\n    <li>and so much more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<a href=\"https://thimpress.com/log/ecommerce-wordpress-theme-adot/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/envato/changelogs.jpg\" alt=\"Adot WordPress Theme Changelog\" /></a>\n\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/forums/forum/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/tf-support.png\" alt=\"Adot | eCommerce WordPress Theme - 4\" /></a> </td>\n<td><a href=\"https://docspress.thimpress.com/adot/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/tf-document.png\" alt=\"Adot | eCommerce WordPress Theme - 5\" /></a>    </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ThimPress/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/face-book.png\" alt=\"Adot | eCommerce WordPress Theme - 6\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://twitter.com/thimpress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/twitter.png?v=3\" alt=\"Adot | eCommerce WordPress Theme - 7\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/+Thimpress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/google.png\" alt=\"Adot | eCommerce WordPress Theme - 8\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/user/thimpress\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/follow-Tf.png?v=3\" alt=\"Adot | eCommerce WordPress Theme - 9\" /></a> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n <h3 id=\"item-description__wordpress-themes-by-thimpress\">WordPress themes by ThimPress</h3>\n <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/education-wordpress-theme-education-wp/14058034\"><img src=\"https://s3.envato.com/files/315458516/preview.__large_preview.png\" alt=\"Education WordPress Theme | Eduma\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/course-builder-wordpress-learning-management-sy