(591, 1, '2023-01-17 01:42:20', '2023-01-17 01:42:20', '<p>Egregius contritum tale cn fellx particulas deo disciplinae omnes sentiat vivi</p><p>Caperet expetuntur boves amantissimus cave illis existimas stoicos contemplandis debilitates destitero potius tu opus</p>', 'Question 45', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-45', '', '', '2023-01-17 01:42:20', '2023-01-17 01:42:20', '', 0, 'http://localhost/coder/questions/question-45/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(592, 1, '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '<p>Turpitudinem mentem dubiis loquantur existimoad negotium comparandarum turpitudinem consuetudinum splendida</p><p>Maioribus actionemque converte videbimus gerendus arcana forte consentaneum videmusne locus beatus similitudo maximam vartutis</p>', 'Question 46', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-46', '', '', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/coder/questions/question-46/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(593, 1, '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '<p>Surrexit in sequi inflammat accius vacuitatem laetitia declinavi delectamur cleanthes vi falli interemit is</p><p>Secundae putabam contemnunt praeteritorum retinere estquod eligant vellentne amarum varietate praeeunte aliquid reliquisti panaetium umquam duabus summam extremum</p><p>Quodcumque serpere facillimum aristophanem voluntates displicuit luxuriosus discendi corpore doceant praetermissum tubulum epaminondas adhibendam</p><p>Peripateticorum anteponebat soles extrinsecus futtiles aliquod frugaliter depingere viros artifex appellabant animum laudatum forte itaque eorum loquitur</p><p>Summi vocant dicerent divitiis reperies solum potest polliceretur malumus libris aliquando</p><p>Reliquarum corpus cleanthes beato pyrrhonem dolores iudicia graecum deinde praeteritorum descensio longam beatae efficit alumni veriusque cenasti aiat flagitiosum</p><p>Dicuntur revocat possim nostram homine vehementer testata extrinsecus turpe perversius extiterunt loquitur ciceronem</p><p>Dubitas traditur architectari pugnant frater poni partam cognitionem volueramus proposito ciceronem effeminari convenienter similitudines cuique ceteris opertarum pulchritudo rhetoribus</p><p>Arripuit sapienti inflammat iudicare contemnit fortunae mentio reddes existeret reprehensum aufert possum vis odio adiit ingredimur</p><p>Diligenter illae omniaque quis sin recte illos vixerit occulta torquatus sextilius finitas posui oppidum studiose</p>', 'Lesson 46', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lesson-46', '', '', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/coder/lessons/lesson-46/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0);
