(645, 1, '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '<p>Coniunctio laudat facilior multoque que doloris est propterea audax fingeres respondeas indicia doctrina</p><p>Indignum nullum vulnera sullae utram resisto patria faciant homerus danda intellegimus commoda</p>', 'Question 72', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-72', '', '', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/coder/questions/question-72/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(646, 1, '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '<p>Mediocri quidem illius clamores tubuli polemonis expetendum rufo oblivisci vacabit sibi quanto videremus</p><p>Et commoda perturbationes etsi delectatus luxuriam totam despiciendis parum sedulo molliorque negabat parvi anquam statuam recuso</p>', 'Question 73', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-73', '', '', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '2023-01-17 01:42:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/coder/questions/question-73/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(647, 1, '2023-01-17 01:42:22', '2023-01-17 01:42:22', '<p>Socium litigiosam stoici negas poterant simplicia omnium sola voluptates agendum fictas videremus dedocendi moriendum fallare semper restatis declaret</p><p>Quavis facinus postumius recusant ei primisque quanto oratione audax constructio iucunda orbus</p>', 'Question 74', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-74', '', '', '2023-01-17 01:42:22', '2023-01-17 01:42:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost/coder/questions/question-74/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
(648, 1, '2023-01-17 01:42:22', '2023-01-17 01:42:22', '<p>Dantur posuisse minime referas egens dignitatem faciliorem pauca deum mentio actus cantibus</p><p>Hieronymus regiones infame minor ingenii praecordiis fruitur progredientibus praeposita crucem utroque extiterunt currit praeteritorum dogmata mitigari me</p>', 'Question 75', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'question-75', '', '', '2023-01-17 01:42:22', '2023-01-17 01:42:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost/coder/questions/question-75/', 0, 'lp_question', '', 0),
