(977, 1, '2023-01-23 06:37:30', '2023-01-23 06:37:30', 'MongoDB is a source-available cross-platform document-oriented database program. Classified as a NoSQL database program, MongoDB uses JSON-like documents with optional schemas. MongoDB is developed by MongoDB Inc. and licensed under the Server Side Public License which is deemed non-free by several distributions.', 'MongoDB', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '96-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-01-23 06:37:30', '2023-01-23 06:37:30', '', 96, 'http://localhost/coder/?p=977', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
